text: Rajmund Csányi (born 22 April 1936) is a Hungarian gymnast. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bucharest
